@startuml
title Functional Cohesion - Module 9 (Shared)

skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #475569
}

package "Shared Module (Functional Cohesion)" {
    class SharedBoundary <<Boundary>> {
        +showDialog()
        +displayNotification()
    }
    class SharedService <<Control>> {
        +normalizeError()
        +formatSharedResponse()
    }
    class SharedUtility <<Entity>> {
        +formatDate()
        +mapApiError()
    }
}

SharedBoundary --> SharedService : delegates shared UI flow
SharedService --> SharedUtility : uses common helpers

note right of SharedService
All classes support reusable
cross-module infrastructure.
end note

@enduml
